::section[headline="How It Works"]

::steps[headline="Three Steps"]
1. **Describe** — Tell the AI what you want
2. **Generate** — SurfDoc spec + surf-parse builds it
3. **Ship** — Live on your domain instantly
::

::

::features[headline="Why SurfDoc"]

### Typed Blocks
37 semantic block types — callouts, decisions, data, metrics, layouts, landing pages.

### Graceful Degradation
Every `.surf` file is readable as plain markdown. No lock-in.

### AI-Native
Designed for AI agents to read, write, and modify without special tooling.

::

::comparison[headline="SurfDoc vs Markdown"]

| Feature | SurfDoc | Markdown |
|---------|---------|----------|
| Typed blocks | Yes | No |
| Structured data | Yes | No |
| Web generation | Yes | No |
| Graceful degradation | Yes | N/A |

::

